snippet: Supposed excerpts from a wryly conceptual “newsletter” on Khalil Rabah’s fictional Palestinian Museum of Natural History and Humankind are on view at e-flux.
abstract: Holland Cotter reviews Pages, 7, 8, 9 exhibit of works from artist Khalil Rabah at e-flux gallery.
